decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Robin\" title=\"Robin\">Robin</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Sam\" title=\"Sam\"><img alt=\"Sam Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/5/52/Sam_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Sam\" title=\"Sam\">Sam</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Sandy\" title=\"Sandy\"><img alt=\"Sandy Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/7/7d/Sandy_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Sandy\" title=\"Sandy\">Sandy</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Sebastian\" title=\"Sebastian\"><img alt=\"Sebastian Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/6/6a/Sebastian_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Sebastian\" title=\"Sebastian\">Sebastian</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Shane\" title=\"Shane\"><img alt=\"Shane Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/b/b4/Shane_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Shane\" title=\"Shane\">Shane</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Vincent\" title=\"Vincent\"><img alt=\"Vincent Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/0/0b/Vincent_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Vincent\" title=\"Vincent\">Vincent</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Willy\" title=\"Willy\"><img alt=\"Willy Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/7/73/Willy_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Willy\" title=\"Willy\">Willy</a></span>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Bundles\">Bundles</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Slime&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Bundles\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>99 Slime is one of the options for the <span style=\"display:inline; margin-right:0;\"><img alt=\"Bundle Purple.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a1/Bundle_Purple.png/24px-Bundle_Purple.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a1/Bundle_Purple.png/36px-Bundle_Purple.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/a/a1/Bundle_Purple.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Bundles#Adventurers_Bundle\" title=\"Bundles\">Adventurer's Bundle</a> in the <a href=\"/Bundles#Boiler_Room\" title=\"Bundles\">Boiler Room</a></span>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recipes\">Recipes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Slime&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Recipes\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable roundedborder\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Image\n</th>\n<th>Name\n</th>\n<th>Description\n</th>\n<th>Ingredient\n</th>\n<th>Equipment\n</th>\n<th>Time\n</th>\n<th>Sell Price\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/File:Green_Slime_Egg.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Green Slime Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/1/1d/Green_Slime_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a></div></div>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/Slime_Egg\" title=\"Slime Egg\">Slime Egg</a>\n</td>\n<td>Can be hatched in a slime incubator.\n</td>\n<td><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r120955\">.mw-parser-output .nametemplate{margin:2px 5px 1px 2px;display:block;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline{margin:2px 0 1px 2px;display:inline;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplate img,.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline img{max-width:none}</style><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Slime.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/38/Slime.png/24px-Slime.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/38/Slime.png/36px-Slime.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/3/38/Slime.png 2x\" /> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Slime</a>&#160;(100)</span>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/File:Slime_Egg-Press.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Slime Egg-Press.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/79/Slime_Egg-Press.png/40px-Slime_Egg-Press.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"40\" height=\"80\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/7/79/Slime_Egg-Press.png 1.5x\" /></a></div></div><a href=\"/Slime_Egg-Press\" title=\"Slime Egg-Press\">Slime Egg-Press</a>\n</td>\n<td><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r120974\">.mw-parser-output .durationtemplate{margin:2px 5px 1px 2px;display:block;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .durationtemplateinline{margin:2px 0 1px 2px;display:inline;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .durationtemplate img,.mw-parser-output .durationtemplateinline img{max-width:none}</style><span class=\"durationtemplate\"><img alt=\"Time Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/24px-Time_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/36px-Time_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/7/70/Time_Icon.png 2x\" /> 1200m (20h)</span>\n</td>\n<td>\n<table>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/File:Green_Slime_Egg.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Green Slime Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/1d/Green_Slime_Egg.png/18px-Green_Slime_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/1d/Green_Slime_Egg.png/27px-Green_Slime_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/1d/Green_Slime_Egg.png/36px-Green_Slime_Egg.png 2x\" /></a> <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"1000\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />1,000g</span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Blue_Slime_Egg.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Blue Slime Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a2/Blue_Slime_Egg.png/18px-Blue_Slime_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a2/Blue_Slime_Egg.png/27px-Blue_Slime_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a2/Blue_Slime_Egg.png/36px-Blue_Slime_Egg.png 2x\" /></a> <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"1750\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />1,750g</span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Red_Slime_Egg.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Red Slime Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/ae/Red_Slime_Egg.png/18px-Red_Slime_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/ae/Red_Slime_Egg.png/27px-Red_Slime_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/a/ae/Red_Slime_Egg.png/36px-Red_Slime_Egg.png 2x\" /></a> <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"2500\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />2,500g</span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Purple_Slime_Egg.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Purple Slime Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/65/Purple_Slime_Egg.png/18px-Purple_Slime_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/65/Purple_Slime_Egg.png/27px-Purple_Slime_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/6/65/Purple_Slime_Egg.png/36px-Purple_Slime_Egg.png 2x\" /></a> <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"5000\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />5,000g</span>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><i>The color of the resulting slime egg is random, but the cheaper ones are more common. See <a href=\"/Slime_Egg-Press\" title=\"Slime Egg-Press\">Slime Egg-Press</a> for the list of probabilities.</i>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Crafting\">Crafting</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Slime&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Crafting\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable sortable roundedborder\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Image\n</th>\n<th>Name\n</th>\n<th>Description\n</th>\n<th>Ingredients\n</th>\n<th>Recipe Source\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/File:Oil_Maker.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Oil Maker.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/c/c5/Oil_Maker.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"96\" /></a></div></div>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/Oil_Maker\" title=\"Oil Maker\">Oil Maker</a>\n</td>\n<td>Makes gourmet truffle oil.\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Slime.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/38/Slime.png/24px-Slime.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/38/Slime.png/36px-Slime.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/3/38/Slime.png 2x\" /> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Slime</a>&#160;(50)</span>\n<p><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Hardwood.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/ed/Hardwood.png/24px-Hardwood.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/ed/Hardwood.png/36px-Hardwood.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/e/ed/Hardwood.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Hardwood\" title=\"Hardwood\">Hardwood</a>&#160;(20)</span>\n<link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Gold Bar.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/4e/Gold_Bar.png/24px-Gold_Bar.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/4e/Gold_Bar.png/36px-Gold_Bar.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/4/4e/Gold_Bar.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Gold_Bar\" title=\"Gold Bar\">Gold Bar</a>&#160;(1)</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td><img alt=\"Farming Skill Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/82/Farming_Skill_Icon.png/24px-Farming_Skill_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/82/Farming_Skill_Icon.png/36px-Farming_Skill_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/8/82/Farming_Skill_Icon.png/48px-Farming_Skill_Icon.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Farming\" title=\"Farming\">Farming</a> Level 8\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/File:Cork_Bobber.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Cork Bobber.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/0/0b/Cork_Bobber.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a></div></div>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/Cork_Bobber\" title=\"Cork Bobber\">Cork Bobber</a>\n</td>\n<td>Slightly increases the size of your \"fishing bar\".\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Wood.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/df/Wood.png/24px-Wood.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/df/Wood.png/36px-Wood.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/d/df/Wood.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Wood\" title=\"Wood\">Wood</a>&#160;(10)</span>\n<p><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Hardwood.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/ed/Hardwood.png/24px-Hardwood.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/ed/Hardwood.png/36px-Hardwood.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/e/ed/Hardwood.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Hardwood\" title=\"Hardwood\">Hardwood</a>&#160;(5)</span>\n<link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Slime.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/38/Slime.png/24px-Slime.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/38/Slime.png/36px-Slime.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/3/38/Slime.png 2x\" /> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Slime</a>&#160;(10)</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td><img alt=\"Fishing Skill Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e7/Fishing_Skill_Icon.png/24px-Fishing_Skill_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e7/Fishing_Skill_Icon.png/36px-Fishing_Skill_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e7/Fishing_Skill_Icon.png/48px-Fishing_Skill_Icon.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Fishing\" title=\"Fishing\">Fishing</a> Level 7\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/File:Slime_Incubator.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Slime Incubator.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/c/c0/Slime_Incubator.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"96\" /></a></div></div>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/Slime_Incubator\" title=\"Slime Incubator\">Slime Incubator</a>\n</td>\n<td>Hatches slimes eggs into slimes. Allows you to raise slimes outdoors.\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Iridium Bar.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/c4/Iridium_Bar.png/24px-Iridium_Bar.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/c4/Iridium_Bar.png/36px-Iridium_Bar.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/c/c4/Iridium_Bar.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Iridium_Bar\" title=\"Iridium Bar\">Iridium Bar</a>&#160;(2)</span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Slime.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/38/Slime.png/24px-Slime.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/38/Slime.png/36px-Slime.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/3/38/Slime.png 2x\" /> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Slime</a>&#160;(100)</span>\n</td>\n<td><img alt=\"Combat Skill Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/cf/Combat_Skill_Icon.png/24px-Combat_Skill_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/cf/Combat_Skill_Icon.png/36px-Combat_Skill_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/c/cf/Combat_Skill_Icon.png/48px-Combat_Skill_Icon.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Combat\" title=\"Combat\">Combat</a> Level 8\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/File:Wild_Bait.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Wild Bait.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/d/da/Wild_Bait.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a></div></div>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/Wild_Bait\" title=\"Wild Bait\">Wild Bait</a> (5)\n</td>\n<td>A unique recipe from Linus that gives you a chance to catch two fish at once.\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Fiber.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/45/Fiber.png/24px-Fiber.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/45/Fiber.png/36px-Fiber.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/4/45/Fiber.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Fiber\" title=\"Fiber\">Fiber</a>&#160;(10)</span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Bug Meat.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/b/b6/Bug_Meat.png/24px-Bug_Meat.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/b/b6/Bug_Meat.png/36px-Bug_Meat.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/b/b6/Bug_Meat.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Bug_Meat\" title=\"Bug Meat\">Bug Meat</a>&#160;(5)</span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Slime.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/38/Slime.png/24px-Slime.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/38/Slime.png/36px-Slime.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/3/38/Slime.png 2x\" /> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Slime</a>&#160;(5)</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"no-wrap\"><p><img alt=\"Linus Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/d/db/Linus_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /> <a href=\"/Linus\" title=\"Linus\">Linus</a>&#160;(4 <img alt=\"HeartIconLarge.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/0/04/HeartIconLarge.png/18px-HeartIconLarge.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/0/04/HeartIconLarge.png/27px-HeartIconLarge.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/0/04/HeartIconLarge.png 2x\" /> Event)</p>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/File:Sturdy_Ring.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Sturdy Ring.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/7/7e/Sturdy_Ring.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a></div></div>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/Sturdy_Ring\" title=\"Sturdy Ring\">Sturdy Ring</a>\n</td>\n<td>Cuts the duration of negative status effects in half.\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Copper Bar.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f1/Copper_Bar.png/24px-Copper_Bar.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f1/Copper_Bar.png/36px-Copper_Bar.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/f/f1/Copper_Bar.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Copper_Bar\" title=\"Copper Bar\">Copper Bar</a>&#160;(2)</span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Bug Meat.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/b/b6/Bug_Meat.png/24px-Bug_Meat.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/b/b6/Bug_Meat.png/36px-Bug_Meat.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/b/b6/Bug_Meat.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Bug_Meat\" title=\"Bug Meat\">Bug Meat</a>&#160;(25)</span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Slime.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/38/Slime.png/24px-Slime.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/38/Slime.png/36px-Slime.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/3/38/Slime.png 2x\" /> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Slime</a>&#160;(25)</span>\n</td>\n<td><img alt=\"Combat Skill Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/cf/Combat_Skill_Icon.png/24px-Combat_Skill_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/cf/Combat_Skill_Icon.png/36px-Combat_Skill_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/c/cf/Combat_Skill_Icon.png/48px-Combat_Skill_Icon.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Skills#Combat\" title=\"Skills\">Combat</a> Level 1\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/File:Monster_Musk.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Monster Musk.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/a/af/Monster_Musk.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a></div></div>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/Monster_Musk\" title=\"Monster Musk\">Monster Musk</a>\n</td>\n<td>Spray this on to draw more monsters out of hiding.\n</td>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Bat Wing.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/35/Bat_Wing.png/24px-Bat_Wing.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/35/Bat_Wing.png/36px-Bat_Wing.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/3/35/Bat_Wing.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Bat_Wing\" title=\"Bat Wing\">Bat Wing</a>&#160;(30)</span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Slime.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/38/Slime.png/24px-Slime.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/38/Slime.png/36px-Slime.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/3/38/Slime.png 2x\" /> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Slime</a>&#160;(30)</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"no-wrap\"><p><img alt=\"Wizard Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/e/e9/Wizard_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /> <a href=\"/Wizard\" title=\"Wizard\">Wizard</a>&#160;(<a href=\"/Quests#Prismatic_Jelly\" title=\"Quests\">Special Order</a>)</p>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Tailoring\">Tailoring</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Slime&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Tailoring\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Slime is used in the spool of the <a href=\"/2_Willow_Lane#Sewing_Machine\" title=\"2 Willow Lane\">Sewing Machine</a> to create a <a href=\"/File:Shirt096.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Shirt096.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/b/b6/Shirt096.png/24px-Shirt096.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/b/b6/Shirt096.png 1.5x\" /></a> <a href=\"/Tailoring\" title=\"Tailoring\">Shirt</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quests\">Quests</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Slime&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Quests\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>20 Slime are requested by <a href=\"/Slimejack\" title=\"Slimejack\">Slimejack</a> in a <a href=\"/Fish_Pond#Quests\" title=\"Fish Pond\">Fish Pond quest</a> to increase the capacity of the pond from 1 to 3.</li>\n<li>5 Slime may be requested by <a href=\"/Bullhead\" title=\"Bullhead\">Bullhead</a> or <a href=\"/Largemouth_Bass\" title=\"Largemouth Bass\">Largemouth Bass</a> in a <a href=\"/Fish_Pond#Quests\" title=\"Fish Pond\">Fish Pond quest</a> to increase the capacity of the pond from 3 to 5.</li>\n<li>99 Slime may be requested by the Raccoon at the <a href=\"/Giant_Stump\" title=\"Giant Stump\">Giant Stump</a> as part of his fifth request, or as part of any request starting with the sixth.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Slime&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.4\" title=\"Version History\">1.4</a>: <a href=\"/Sturdy_Ring\" title=\"Sturdy Ring\">Sturdy Ring</a> now uses 25 Slime to craft.  Slime can now be used in Tailoring. Can be requested in <a href=\"/Fish_Pond#Quests\" title=\"Fish Pond\">Fish Pond quests</a>. Can be produced by Fish Ponds.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.5\" title=\"Version History\">1.5</a>: Added Monster Musk recipe.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.6\" title=\"Version History\">1.6</a>: May now be requested by the Raccoon. Is no longer a possible Midnight Carp Fish Pond request.</li></ul>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" id=\"navbox\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/Animals\" title=\"Animals\">Animals</a> and Produce\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Coop\" title=\"Coop\">Coop</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Chicken\" title=\"Chicken\">Chicken</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Egg\" title=\"Egg\">Egg</a> • <a href=\"/Large_Egg\" title=\"Large Egg\">Large Egg</a> • <a href=\"/Egg\" title=\"Egg\">Brown Egg</a> • <a href=\"/Large_Egg\" title=\"Large Egg\">Large Brown Egg</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Dinosaur\" title=\"Dinosaur\">Dinosaur</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Dinosaur_Egg\" title=\"Dinosaur Egg\">Dinosaur Egg</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Duck\" title=\"Duck\">Duck</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Duck_Egg\" title=\"Duck Egg\">Duck Egg</a> • <a href=\"/Duck_Feather\" title=\"Duck Feather\">Duck Feather</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Golden_Chicken\" title=\"Golden Chicken\">Golden Chicken</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Golden_Egg\" title=\"Golden Egg\">Golden Egg</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Rabbit\" title=\"Rabbit\">Rabbit</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Wool\" title=\"Wool\">Wool</a> • <a href=\"/Rabbit%27s_Foot\" title=\"Rabbit&#39;s Foot\">Rabbit's Foot</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Void_Chicken\" title=\"Void Chicken\">Void Chicken</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Void_Egg\" title=\"Void Egg\">Void Egg</a>)</sup>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Barn\" title=\"Barn\">Barn</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Cow\" title=\"Cow\">Cow</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Milk\" title=\"Milk\">Milk</a> • <a href=\"/Large_Milk\" title=\"Large Milk\">Large Milk</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Goat\" title=\"Goat\">Goat</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Goat_Milk\" title=\"Goat Milk\">Goat Milk</a> • <a href=\"/Large_Goat_Milk\" title=\"Large Goat Milk\">Large Goat Milk</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Sheep\" title=\"Sheep\">Sheep</a>  <sup>(<a href=\"/Wool\" title=\"Wool\">Wool</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Ostrich\" title=\"Ostrich\">Ostrich</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Ostrich_Egg\" title=\"Ostrich Egg\">Ostrich Egg</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Pig\" title=\"Pig\">Pig</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Truffle\" title=\"Truffle\">Truffle</a>)</sup>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Fish_Pond\" title=\"Fish Pond\">Fish Pond</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Fish\" title=\"Fish\">Fish</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Roe\" title=\"Roe\">Roe</a>)</sup>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Slime_Hutch\" title=\"Slime Hutch\">Slime Hutch</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Slimes\" title=\"Slimes\">Slimes</a> <sup>(<a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Slime</a> • <a href=\"/Slime_Ball\" title=\"Slime Ball\">Slime Ball</a> • <a href=\"/Slime_Egg\" title=\"Slime Egg\">Slime Egg</a>)</sup>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Other\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Animals#Cat_or_Dog\" title=\"Animals\">Cat</a> • <a href=\"/Animals#Cat_or_Dog\" title=\"Animals\">Dog</a> • <a href=\"/Animals#Horse\" title=\"Animals\">Horse</a> • <a href=\"/Animals#Additional_Pets\" title=\"Animals\">Turtle</a>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260413191819\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.207 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.234 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 12063/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 19904/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1791/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 13/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 6784/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.004/7.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 638 KB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  118.283      1 -total\n 40.85%   48.313      8 Template:Description\n 22.41%   26.511      1 Template:Infobox\n 18.60%   21.996     17 Template:Name\n  9.01%   10.654      1 Template:Tprice\n  4.68%    5.533      1 Template:GiftsByItem\n  3.34%    3.945      1 Template:Bundle\n  3.14%    3.711      1 Template:Duration\n  2.79%    3.302      3 Template:History\n  2.55%    3.011      7 Template:Price\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:1772-0!canonical and timestamp 20260413191819 and revision id 190637\n -->\n</div>",
      "wikitext": "{{Infobox\n|eng       = Slime\n|source    = [[Slimes]] • [[Krobus]] • [[Slime Ball]] • [[Traveling Cart]] • [[Fish Pond]]\n|sellprice = 5\n|quality   = false\n}}\n{{For|the monster from which this item drops|Slimes|R=This page is for the item drop.}}\n'''Slime''' is a [[Monster Loot]] item which is dropped by [[Slimes]]. Killing a single [[Slimes|Slime]] can drop up to two Slime. Slime can also be obtained from [[Slime Ball]]s or purchased from [[Krobus]] for {{Price|10}} on [[Days of the Week#Monday|Mondays]] (up to 50 per Monday).  It may randomly appear in the [[Traveling Cart]] for {{tprice|15}}. A [[Slimejack]] [[Fish Pond]] may also produce 10, 30, or 50 Slime daily when the population reaches 9.\n\n==Gifting==\n{{GiftsByItem\n|hate=Robin,Demetrius,Maru,Sebastian,Linus,Leo,Pierre,Caroline,Abigail,Alex,George,Evelyn,Lewis,Clint,Penny,Pam,Emily,Haley,Jas,Vincent,Jodi,Kent,Sam,Leah,Shane,Marnie,Elliott,Gus,Dwarf,Harvey,Sandy,Willy,Krobus\n|dislike=Wizard\n}}\n\n==Bundles==\n99 Slime is one of the options for the {{Bundle|adventurer||y}}.\n\n==Recipes==\n{| class=\"wikitable roundedborder\"\n!Image\n!Name\n!Description\n!Ingredient\n!Equipment\n!Time\n!Sell Price\n|-\n|[[File:Green Slime Egg.png|center]]\n|[[Slime Egg]]\n|{{Description|Slime Egg}}\n|{{Name|Slime|100}}\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|[[File:Slime Egg-Press.png|center|40px]][[Slime Egg-Press]]\n|{{Duration|1200m (20h)}}\n|\n{|\n|class=\"no-wrap\"|[[File:Green Slime Egg.png|18px]] {{Price|1000}}\n|-\n|[[File:Blue Slime Egg.png|18px]] {{Price|1750}}\n|-\n|[[File:Red Slime Egg.png|18px]] {{Price|2500}}\n|-\n|[[File:Purple Slime Egg.png|18px]] {{Price|5000}}\n|}\n|}\n\n''The color of the resulting slime egg is random, but the cheaper ones are more common. See [[Slime Egg-Press]] for the list of probabilities.''\n\n==Crafting==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable roundedborder\"\n!Image\n!Name\n!Description\n!Ingredients\n!Recipe Source\n|-\n|[[File:Oil Maker.png|center]]\n|[[Oil Maker]]\n|{{Description|Oil Maker}}\n|{{Name|Slime|50}}\n{{Name|Hardwood|20}}\n{{Name|Gold Bar|1}}\n|[[File:Farming Skill Icon.png|24px|link=]] [[Farming]] Level 8\n|-\n|[[File:Cork Bobber.png|center]]\n|[[Cork Bobber]]\n|{{Description|Cork Bobber}}\n|{{Name|Wood|10}}\n{{Name|Hardwood|5}}\n{{Name|Slime|10}}\n|[[File:Fishing Skill Icon.png|24px|link=]] [[Fishing]] Level 7\n|-\n|[[File:Slime Incubator.png|center]]\n|[[Slime Incubator]]\n|{{Description|Slime Incubator}}\n|{{Name|Iridium Bar|2}}{{Name|Slime|100}}\n|[[File:Combat Skill Icon.png|24px|link=]] [[Combat]] Level 8\n|-\n|[[File:Wild Bait.png|center]]\n|[[Wild Bait]] (5)\n|{{Description|Wild Bait}}\n|{{Name|Fiber|10}}{{Name|Bug Meat|5}}{{Name|Slime|5}}\n|class=\"no-wrap\"|{{NPC|Linus|4 [[File:HeartIconLarge.png|18px|link=]] Event}}\n|-\n|[[File:Sturdy Ring.png|center]]\n|[[Sturdy Ring]]\n|{{Description|Sturdy Ring}}\n|{{Name|Copper Bar|2}}{{Name|Bug Meat|25}}{{Name|Slime|25}}\n|[[File:Combat Skill Icon.png|24px|link=]] [[Skills#Combat|Combat]] Level 1\n|-\n|[[File:Monster Musk.png|center]]\n|[[Monster Musk]]\n|{{Description|Monster Musk}}\n|{{Name|Bat Wing|30}}{{Name|Slime|30}}\n|class=\"no-wrap\"|{{NPC|Wizard|[[Quests#Prismatic Jelly|Special Order]]}}\n|-\n|}\n\n==Tailoring==\nSlime is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create a [[File:Shirt096.png|24px]] [[Tailoring|Shirt]].\n\n==Quests==\n*20 Slime are requested by [[Slimejack]] in a [[Fish Pond#Quests|Fish Pond quest]] to increase the capacity of the pond from 1 to 3.\n*5 Slime may be requested by [[Bullhead]] or [[Largemouth Bass]] in a [[Fish Pond#Quests|Fish Pond quest]] to increase the capacity of the pond from 3 to 5.\n*99 Slime may be requested by the Raccoon at the [[Giant Stump]] as part of his fifth request, or as part of any request starting with the sixth.\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.4|[[Sturdy Ring]] now uses 25 Slime to craft.  Slime can now be used in Tailoring. Can be requested in [[Fish Pond#Quests|Fish Pond quests]]. Can be produced by Fish Ponds.}}\n{{History|1.5|Added Monster Musk recipe.}}\n{{History|1.6|May now be requested by the Raccoon. Is no longer a possible Midnight Carp Fish Pond request.}}\n\n{{NavboxAnimals}}\n\n[[Category:Animal Products]]\n[[Category:Monster Loot]]\n\n[[de:Schleim]]\n[[es:Baba]]\n[[fr:Slime]]\n[[it:Melma]]\n[[ja:スライム]]\n[[ko:슬라임]]\n[[hu:Ragacs]]\n[[pt:Gosma]]\n[[ru:Слизь]]\n[[tr:Balçıkça]]\n[[zh:史莱姆泥]]"
